Package: corrector
Title: Automatic Grading of R Coding Exercises
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Pablo", "Vena", email = "vena.pablo@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Pablo Vena [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Pablo Vena <vena.pablo@gmail.com>
Description: Grades student R coding exercises against professor-written test
    functions. Accepts a directory or zip archive of submissions, matches each
    exercise file to its test file, and returns a pass/fail data frame.
    Provides optional export to CSV or Google Sheets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/anevolbap/corrector
BugReports: https://github.com/anevolbap/corrector/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
